'''盧安達航空'''（<span title="「RwandAir」這個拼字是英語跟盧旺達語一樣的" class="rt-commentedText">{{lang|rw|'''RwandAir'''}}</span>）是一家以[[盧安達|盧安達]][[基加利|基加利]]為基地的[[國家航空公司|國家航空公司]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://centreforaviation.com/analysis/rwandair-plans-further-regional-expansion-in-2015-and-launch-of-long-haul-services-in-2017-202148 |title=CAPA Centre for Aviation. Retrieved 2 December 2015. |accessdate=2016-07-24 |archive-date=2015-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151107035237/http://centreforaviation.com/analysis/rwandair-plans-further-regional-expansion-in-2015-and-launch-of-long-haul-services-in-2017-202148 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，成立於2002年，於2003年4月27日正式營運，主要經營國內航線及東非、中非、南非與中東等地的國際航線，近年也開始飛航歐洲地區的航線，其樞紐為[[基加利國際機場|基加利國際機場]]。

==歷史==

===籌建===
1994年[[卢旺达种族灭绝|盧旺達大屠殺]]結束後，當時的盧旺達政府一直打算重新開設一間新的國家航空公司，以取代因大屠殺事件而停運的舊盧旺達航空。

在1997年，烏干達的聯盟航空曾一度表示有意與盧旺達政府合作，以開辨公私合營的新盧旺達航空<ref name="Six">{{cite web |url=https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1997/1997%20-%203062.html?search=air%20rwanda |title=Alliance spreads into Central Africa |last=Yates |first=Chris |access-date=2018-05-18 |publisher=Flightglobal.com Archiving Air Transport Magazine |date=1997 |format=Archived from the Original |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305032411/https://www.flightglobal.com/pdfarchive/view/1997/1997%20-%203062.html?search=air%20rwanda |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但最終該公司在2000年倒閉，合營計劃亦因而告吹，改為由政府獨資籌建。直至2002年12月1日，新盧旺達航空正式以「盧旺達快運航空」名義成立。

===2000年代：早年發展及第一次私有化===
自盧旺達快運航空在2003年首航以後，其航點不斷擴展，並擴展至經營國外航線。

至2009年6月，「盧旺達快運航空」正式改名為「盧旺達航空」，以強調該公司為一間幹線航空公司的形象<ref name="Eight">{{cite web |url=http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/advertorial/466 |title=RwandAir changing country's aviation industry through enhanced aviation skills |access-date=2018-05-18 |date=2014-04-25 |author=Peterson Tumwebaze |newspaper=New Times (Rwanda) |location=Kigali |archive-date=2021-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210802160216/https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/advertorial/466 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。翌年，盧旺達航空亦開設[[飛行常客獎勵計劃|飛行常客獎勵計劃]]。

而在2000年代內，盧旺達政府亦曾打算將此公司，以標售股權方式實行私有化，並擬於2013年完成。然而，由於未達底價，盧旺達航空的第一次私有化計劃最後告吹<ref>{{cite web |access-date=2018-05-18 |url=http://www.rnanews.com/politics/4122-rwandair-to-be-sold-after-becoming-profitable-finance-minister |date=2010-09-04 |publisher=Rwanda News Agency (RNA) |author=RNA Reporter |location=Kigali |title=RwandAir to be sold after becoming profitable – Finance Minister |archive-date=2018-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180519120911/http://www.rnanews.com/politics/4122-rwandair-to-be-sold-after-becoming-profitable-finance-minister |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===2010年代：持續擴展===
2010-12年間，盧旺達航空分別接收[[波音737|波音737-500]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/23231 |title=Another RwandAir Boeing arrives |access-date=2018-05-18 |date=2010-04-23 |author=Peterson Tumwebaze |location=Kigali |newspaper=New Times (Rwanda) |archive-date=2021-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210802154418/https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/23231 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、波音737-800<ref>{{cite web |access-date=2018-05-18 |url=http://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/84787 |title=RwandAir's new Boeing 737-800NB plane lands |date=2011-04-28 |newspaper=New Times (Rwanda) |location=Kigali |author=Peterson Tumwebaze |archive-date=2021-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210802154708/https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/84787 |dead-url=no }}</ref>及CRJ-900NG客機，當中737-800為該公司首次接收的全新飛機，而CRJ-900NG用於取代機齡較舊的CRJ-200<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.flightcommagazine.com/single-post/2017/05/03/RwandAir---Daring-to-dream|title=RwandAir: Daring to dream|date=2017-05-03|access-date=2018-05-18|publisher=Flightcommagazine.com|author=Flightcommagazine.com|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124143108/https://www.flightcommagazine.com/single-post/2017/05/03/RwandAir---Daring-to-dream|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在機隊方面，此公司於2013年2月開辦往返阿克拉、開普敦、哈拉雷、朱巴和桑給巴爾的航線<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.newsday.co.zw/2013/02/13/rwandair-eyes-harare-route/|title=RwandAir eyes Harare route|access-date=2016-01-26|last=Business Reporter|newspaper=NewsDay Quoting Bloomberg News|location=Harare|date=2013-02-13|archive-date=2017-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170212162307/https://www.newsday.co.zw/2013/02/13/rwandair-eyes-harare-route/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於2017年獲准開設往返貝寧柯多努的航線<ref>{{cite web |access-date=2018-05-18 |first=David |url=https://www.routesonline.com/news/29/breaking-news/274134/rwandair-launches-cotonou-hub-as-benin-and-rwanda-plan-new-airline/ |title=RwandAir launches Cotonou hub as Benin and Rwanda plan new airline |last=Casey |date=2017-08-03 |publisher=Routesonline.com |location=Manchester, United Kingdom |archive-date=2021-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210803120727/https://www.routesonline.com/news/29/breaking-news/274134/rwandair-launches-cotonou-hub-as-benin-and-rwanda-plan-new-airline/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2015年5月，盧安達航空正式成為IATA成員<ref>{{cite web|access-date=2016-01-26|url=http://www.busiweek.com/index1.php?Ctp=2&pI=4725&pLv=3&srI=58&spI=24|title=Global umbrella gives RwandAir kudos|date=2016-01-24|first=Agnes|last=Bateta|newspaper=East African Business Week|location=Kampala|archive-date=2018-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180426011721/http://www.busiweek.com/index1.php?Ctp=2&pI=4725&pLv=3&srI=58&spI=24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===2020年代：第二次私有化===
於2020年2月，[[卡塔爾航空|卡塔爾航空]]正式收購盧旺達航空49%的股權，以實施第二次私有化，而另外51%仍由盧旺達政府持有<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nytimes.com/reuters/2020/02/05/business/05reuters-qatar-aviation-qatar-airways-m-a.html|title=Qatar Airways in Talks to Buy 49% RwandAir Stake, Interested in Increasing LATAM Investment|access-date=2020-02-05|work=The New York Times|archive-date=2020-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200206095411/https://www.nytimes.com/reuters/2020/02/05/business/05reuters-qatar-aviation-qatar-airways-m-a.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至2021年3月，此公司的私有化工作進入最後階段<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.logupdateafrica.com/govt-in-final-talks-with-qatar-airways-over-rwandair-equity-aviation|title=Govt in final talks with Qatar Airways over RwandAir equity|publisher=Logistics Update Africa|date=2021-03-26|access-date=2021-08-03|archive-date=2021-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210803114359/https://www.logupdateafrica.com/govt-in-final-talks-with-qatar-airways-over-rwandair-equity-aviation|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ch-aviation.com/portal/news/101746-kigali-in-final-talks-with-qatar-over-rwandair-equity|title=Kigali in final talks with Qatar over RwandAir equity|publisher=ch-Aviation|date=2021-03-22|access-date=2021-08-03|archive-date=2021-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210701225150/https://www.ch-aviation.com/portal/news/101746-kigali-in-final-talks-with-qatar-over-rwandair-equity|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於隨後完成。

